== Unverifiable information ==
When the First Presbyterian Church of Saranac Lake was being built, Shepard covered the church’s $900 debt and paid for a manse, stable, and church bell. Shepard Avenue in Saranac Lake, New York is named for him. (Source: http://localwiki.net/hsl/Elliott_Shepard) --[[User:Ɱ|<span style="text-shadow:#BBBBBB 0.1em 0.1em 0.1em; class = FA"><font color="darkgreen">'''ɱ'''</font></span>]] [[User talk:Ɱ|<font color="darkgreen">(talk)</font>]] 21:28, 11 August 2014 (UTC)
